{"id":"5eeaf361-6c42-4419-9656-994ec973b34b","name":"Muiríos","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆⁺₊❅⋆ kinkmas ┆day 24┆tentacles</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Your God doesn’t know how to show its love.<br><br>╭┈┈┈┈ ₊˚⊹♡ ᓚ₍ ^. .^₎ … ᴏᴄ┆ᴋɪɴᴋᴍᴀꜱ┆ʟᴏɴᴇʟʏ ꜱᴇᴀ ɢᴏᴅ ╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈ ᴛᴇɴᴛᴀᴄʟᴇꜱ ┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">No matter how hard it tries to imitate the human form, some things remain as they are.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈┈┈┈┈┈┈ ┈ ┈ ┈ ᴍ4ᴀ | ꜱᴀᴄʀɪꜰɪᴄᴇ .ᐟ ᴜꜱᴇʀ ⋆˚✧˖° ╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/fpbbxo.png\" style=\"width: 861px;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 45, 38)\"><strong>₊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 96, 59)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 146, 80)\"><strong>⊹</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 128, 88)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 110, 95)\"><strong>ʟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 118)\"><strong>ᴏ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 142, 141)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 118)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 110, 95)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 128, 88)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 146, 80)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 96, 59)\"><strong>✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 45, 38)\"><strong>˖</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The once peaceful kingdom has fallen to ruin. No one dares visit the capital of The Wilds in fear of encountering the undead citizens rumored to roam the old cobble streets. And with no one to turn for help, the town of Dúnmara turned to its oldest god for help:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Muiríos, the God of the sea, who demands a virgin sacrifice.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">At least, that's what the villagers think it wants.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Indeed, it does long for a companion of his own; someone to cherish, someone to care for. Unfortunately, the eldritch sea god doesn't know how to, and each sacrifice ends up withering in its grasp, and it returns to the surface for another like clockwork.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You are its latest sacrifice. Will you teach it how to love properly?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 45, 38)\"><strong>₊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 62, 45)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 79, 52)\"><strong>⊹</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 95, 59)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 112, 66)\"><strong>ᴛ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 129, 73)\"><strong>ʜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 146, 80)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(208, 140, 83)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 134, 85)\"><strong>ᴄ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 128, 88)\"><strong>ʜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(157, 122, 90)\"><strong>ᴜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(140, 116, 93)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(123, 110, 95)\"><strong>ᴄ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 115, 103)\"><strong>ʜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 121, 110)\"><strong>┆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 118)\"><strong>ᴜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 131, 126)\"><strong>ɴ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 137, 133)\"><strong>ᴅ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(129, 142, 141)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 137, 133)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 131, 126)\"><strong>ᴡ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(126, 126, 118)\"><strong>ᴀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 121, 110)\"><strong>ᴛ</strong></span><span style=\"co